workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
Friends don't let friends skip leg day – and this quad, hammy and glute-burner won't let you off the hook.


You'll be doing new moves, so practice with the tutorial first. Then make sure you do the warm-up, because you're gonna need it.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Get your lower body primed to work with Bobby.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Your hamstrings and back are about to discover what real work feels like. Pace yourself – you're doing 5 sets.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Lock in your tempo for maximum glute burn.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Split squats switch on every key muscle in your legs and get your core working overtime to maintain balance.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Stick with Bobby through back-to-back supersets that will get your legs burning.

groups.title: Round 5
groups.summary: Pump up your quads and define your calves.
